prefdata[prefdata$trialtot<401,'condition'] = 'fml'
smalltdata[smalltdata$trialtot<401,'condition'] = 'fml'
pilotdata = filter(pilotdata, subj != 39)
pilotdata[pilotdata$trialtot<101,'condition'] = 'fml'

smalltdata = filter(smalltdata,trial<200)

fml_plot <- function(data, variable, labels, group_meth){
  data$variable = data[,variable]
  
  if (group_meth == 'Subject'){
    g <- ggplot()+
      geom_smooth(data=data,
                  aes(x = trial,
                      y = variable,
                      color = factor(subj)),
                  method = 'loess')+
      facet_wrap(~factor(condition))
  } else if (group_meth == 'Condition'){
    g <- ggplot()+
      geom_smooth(data=prefdata,
                  aes(x = trial,
                      y = movedur,
                      color = factor(condition)),
                  method = 'loess')
  }
  
  g <- g+
    labs(title = labels['title'],
         y = labels['ylab'],
         x = labels['xlab'],
         color = group_meth)
  
  return(g)
  
}



fml_plot_delc <- function(data, variable, labels, group_meth){
  data$variable = data[,variable]
  
  if (group_meth == 'Subject'){
    g <- ggplot()+
      geom_smooth(data=data,
                  aes(x = trial,
                      y = variable,
                      color = factor(subj)),
                  method = 'loess')+
      facet_wrap(~factor(delcond))
  } else if (group_meth == 'Condition'){
    g <- ggplot()+
      geom_smooth(data=prefdata,
                  aes(x = trial,
                      y = movedur,
                      color = factor(delcond)),
                  method = 'loess')+
    scale_color_manual(values = viridis(9))
  }
  
  g <- g+
    labs(title = labels['title'],
         y = labels['ylab'],
         x = labels['xlab'],
         color = group_meth)
  
  return(g)
}
